<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 Haleloia, deraina
 Andriamanitray,
 Mpanjaka fototr'aina,
 Mpikarakara anay,
 Ny zava-boahary
 Dia eo an-tananao,
 Ka tena lavorary
 Ny fandaharanao.

[V2]
 Haleloia, deraina
 Hianao, Mpamonjinay
 Nijaly, noratraina,
 Ka maty solonay,
 Anefa naharesy
 Ny fahavalonay,
 Natsangana handresy
 Mba ho fiainanay.

[V3]
 Haleloia, deraina
 Hianao, Fanahy ô !
 Ny herinao ny aina
 Hamelona tokoa ;
 Hianao mikarakara
 Ny fiangonanao,
 Manova, manatsara
 Izao tontolo izao.

[V4]
 Haleloia, deraina
 Ny Telo Izay Iray !
 Hobina sy hiraina,
 Fa Andriamanitray,
 He, Tompo foto-tsoa
 Iainanay atý,
 Fa ho izany koa
 Mandrakizay doria.</lyrics>
<title>Haleloia, deraina FFPM197</title>
<hymn_number>197</hymn_number>
<author>A.H. Mann</author>
</song>